11:55.600 --> 11:59.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think he has the bully
pulpit. He has a great deal of
influence with the Republican

11:59.333 --> 12:04.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Party on both the House
