12:48.866 --> 12:52.733 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SEN. RAND PAUL: You
know, I think there are
various ways you can
characterize both Republican

12:52.733 --> 12:55.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
