13:14.566 --> 13:19.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, characterizing something as
mean or generous I think goes
to people's motives, and I think

13:19.400 --> 13:24.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
it is sort of why we have such
an angry country now. We think
that people have ill motives.

13:24.000 --> 13:28.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But I think Republicans want
people to have health insurance.
We want people to be healthy.

13:28.633 --> 13:33.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So do Democrats. We just believe
in a different type of economic
system or different types

13:33.000 --> 13:37.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of limitations of government
or more expansive government
and how we can do it.

13:37.666 --> 13:40.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: One of the
things, Senator Paul, you have
talked about wanting to do

13:40.600 --> 13:45.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
