13:53.833 --> 13:55.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
SEN. RAND PAUL: Right.

13:55.866 --> 13:59.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: It's a transfer,
