14:03.033 --> 14:07.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SEN. RAND PAUL: No, we
already do quite a bit of
that, and it's call Medicaid.

14:07.033 --> 14:12.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The problem or the
fundamental flaw of
Obamacare was that they put
regulations on the insurance,

14:14.133 --> 14:17.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
about 12 regulations,
which increased the
cost of the insurance.
And so President Obama

14:17.433 --> 14:21.733 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
