worried about these Medicaid
cuts in this legislation.

15:31.333 --> 15:32.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
SEN. RAND PAUL: Right.

15:32.566 --> 15:34.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Where
is the common ground?

15:34.600 --> 15:36.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SEN. RAND PAUL: Well,
