16:13.133 --> 16:15.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Right.

16:15.200 --> 16:17.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SEN. RAND PAUL: We could do that
