really good economics. What it

16:17.766 --> 16:22.566 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
is, is, you're simply
transferring money from
the ordinary, average
taxpayers to very wealthy

16:23.166 --> 16:25.266 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
corporations.

16:25.266 --> 16:28.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But, Senator,
