16:35.533 --> 16:38.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I still don't see where the
middle ground is between you,
other Republicans, and certainly

16:39.266 --> 16:41.266 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
with Democrats.

16:41.266 --> 16:44.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SEN. RAND PAUL: Actually, the
