Paul of Kentucky, we thank you.

17:33.900 --> 17:38.900 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
SEN. RAND PAUL: Thank you.

17:41.333 --> 17:46.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The White House
today reinforced a stark warning
to the government of Syria's

17:48.400 --> 17:52.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Bashar al-Assad against
using chemical weapons.

17:52.466 --> 17:56.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Last night, the administration
announced that the U.S. had
detected -- quote -- "potential

17:56.800 --> 18:01.200 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
