WARREN BUFFETT: Yes.

22:15.600 --> 22:16.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: ...
for people like you.

22:16.400 --> 22:18.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
WARREN BUFFETT: Yes.

22:18.466 --> 22:22.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
