$19 million-something.

24:36.400 --> 24:38.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
WARREN BUFFETT: Right.

24:38.000 --> 24:40.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF:
Nineteen-and-a-half
million last year.

24:40.033 --> 24:44.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
