in past, in the past.

25:04.100 --> 25:07.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And it's even worse than
you say, Judy, because
you're looking at what
that couple would pay

25:07.666 --> 25:12.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in federal income tax. But they
are also paying payroll taxes,
in overwhelming cases. And

25:14.600 --> 25:18.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
