percent tax, you know, just from
Social -- just from the Social

25:19.833 --> 25:24.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Security that she and
her employer pay, but
it's kind of incredible.

25:26.500 --> 25:28.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And now they want to cut it.
No, they want to cut it for
me. I mean, you know, they -- I

25:28.733 --> 25:31.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
