that deserves a cut.

25:31.433 --> 25:35.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, they --
the Republicans are talking
about lowering taxes...

25:35.900 --> 25:36.900 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
WARREN BUFFETT: Absolutely.

25:36.900 --> 25:38.933 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: ... on the...

25:38.933 --> 25:40.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WARREN BUFFETT: They want to
cut my tax 17 percent. They saw
those figures and were shocked

25:40.266 --> 25:41.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
