this year. I don't know any
case where our competitiveness

26:58.633 --> 27:02.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
is being hurt by the federal
income tax rate on corporations.

27:02.033 --> 27:04.633 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Estate
taxes, a thought about that?

27:04.633 --> 27:08.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WARREN BUFFETT: Oh, estate
taxes, I mean, I -- you hear
people call it the death tax.

27:08.200 --> 27:12.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
There are going to be
two-and-a-half million
people die in the
United States this year.

27:12.300 --> 27:17.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
How many estate tax returns
are there going to be? Probably
about 5,000. And the interesting

27:19.333 --> 27:21.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
