have any of the Cayman Islands

28:21.966 --> 28:25.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
or anything like that stuff.
But we follow the law, and we
got a million shareholders.

28:25.333 --> 28:28.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think they probably
expect us to do that. That
doesn't mean I don't think the

28:28.466 --> 28:30.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
law shouldn't be
changed in some way.

28:30.533 --> 28:33.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But I follow the law in terms
of my personal return. I do
not send an extra $5 million

28:33.766 --> 28:35.800 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to the Treasury.

28:35.800 --> 28:40.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Your
philanthropy, we have
talked about it a little
bit. It's legendary.

28:42.033 --> 28:46.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You and Bill Gates, Melinda
Gates have come together and,
I guess, broken all records

28:47.366 --> 28:49.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
imaginable for giving.

28:49.433 --> 28:53.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
At the same time, it's being
pointed out that you're also
making -- you first made that

28:54.800 --> 28:55.866 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
pledge, what, 10, 11 years ago.

28:55.866 --> 28:56.966 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
WARREN BUFFETT: 2006, yes.

28:56.966 --> 28:58.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: 2006.

28:58.933 --> 29:02.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You're now making so much
more even than you did then.
People are saying, well, wait a

29:04.333 --> 29:05.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
