going to be giving more away?

29:05.266 --> 29:07.300 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
How do you think about that?

29:07.300 --> 29:09.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WARREN BUFFETT: Well, I have
got it set up so that, if I make
more, I do give more, because

29:09.733 --> 29:14.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
