setting up -- and, actually,
they can't use it for endowments

29:19.333 --> 29:24.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
or anything. It has to be
spent within 10 years, really,
after my estate's closed, but

29:25.066 --> 29:27.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
call it after I die.

29:27.133 --> 29:30.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: How
much influence do you
think you had on other,
others with wealth, with

29:32.333 --> 29:35.766 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
