generous as you have been?

29:35.766 --> 29:38.300 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WARREN BUFFETT: Well, a lot of
people come back to me on that.

29:38.300 --> 29:43.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And basically, I said, you
know, if you're extremely rich,
and you have got children,

29:45.200 --> 29:47.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
