can buy anything.

30:25.666 --> 30:30.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And once they move into the
hands of people who are working
like hell on getting something

30:32.666 --> 30:37.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
accomplished in areas I want
them to -- you know, I love
the idea of getting them used,

30:38.033 --> 30:40.100 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
