30:40.100 --> 30:43.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: You said it
wouldn't make you happy to have
a hundred, 200 homes and yachts

30:43.033 --> 30:45.800 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and so forth. What does
make Warren Buffett happy?

30:45.800 --> 30:48.366 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WARREN BUFFETT: I just have
a lot of fun doing my job.

30:48.366 --> 30:52.766 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I mean, I can do anything
I want, basically,
as long as it doesn't
involve athletic ability,

30:52.766 --> 30:53.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
or something like that.

30:53.766 --> 30:55.833 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

30:55.833 --> 30:57.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WARREN BUFFETT: But if it's
something I can buy, I can
buy anything, basically.

30:57.833 --> 31:02.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I have been on 400-foot yachts,
and I have - - I have lived
the life a little bit with

31:04.233 --> 31:06.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
people that have 10 homes and
everything. And I live in the
same house I bought in 1958.

31:06.433 --> 31:11.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And if I could spend $100
million on a house that would
make me a lot happier, I would

31:11.200 --> 31:13.166 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
do it.

31:13.166 --> 31:16.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But, for me, that's the happiest
House In the world. And it's
because it's got memories,

31:16.533 --> 31:20.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and people come back, and all
